txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Monstrous wings from the birds surrounding the outpost of Gwingris. You can return the items to Maedlathron at Gwingris in Eregion for reward.
'This is a good thing you have done. Thank you.'
'The birds near this settlement are nothing more than spies for the Enemy. We must defeat them and cull their number. Bring us their wings.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Monstrous Wings
Maedlathron awaits the return of a collection of monstrous wings at the Elf-encampment at Gwingris.
Deliver the monstrous wings to Maedlathron in Gwingris within Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver monstrous wings from the birds near and surrounding the Elf-encampment of Gwingris to the Elf Maedlathron.
Wanted: Monstrous wings from the birds surrounding the outpost of Gwingris.
